// reynard: route persona surfaces that upstream Camoufox navigator-spoofing.patch
// would own through the engine config (REYNARD_CONFIG, with CAMOU_CONFIG fallback),
// because that patch does NOT apply on Firefox 150. Each override is read BEFORE the
// stock path and is a no-op when the key is absent, so non-reynard builds are unchanged.
//
//   navigator.webdriver            Navigator::Webdriver() returns the config bool before
//                                  the remote-agent check (BiDi otherwise forces true).
//   navigator.userAgent            BOTH the instance Navigator::GetUserAgent getter AND
//                                  the static GetUserAgent(window,doc,...) overload that
//                                  WorkerNavigator routes through (closes worker-UA drift).
//   navigator.hardwareConcurrency  BOTH Navigator::HardwareConcurrency() (window) AND
//                                  WorkerNavigator::HardwareConcurrency() (worker); the
//                                  stock path leaks the HOST core count — a datacenter
//                                  tell Arkose reads inside its proof-of-work worker.
//
// moz.build adds /camoucfg to dom/base and dom/workers LOCAL_INCLUDES so the header-only
// MaskConfig.hpp resolves in both realms.
// Regenerate: (cd camoufox-*/ && git diff unpatched -- dom/base/Navigator.cpp \
//   dom/base/moz.build dom/workers/WorkerNavigator.cpp dom/workers/moz.build)
